  "texts": [
    "The adoption of the PRISMA aimed to certify robustness and reduce bias in the review procedure (Demir 2021).",
    "The collected data underwent analysis using topic modeling and bibliometrics, incorporating a statistical trend examination and social network analysis (SNA).",
    "An elaborate description of the procedure is presented below.",
    "This study systematically searched the literature in the Web of Science (WoS) database.",
    "The search terms (Table 2) used in this study were derived from previous reviews related to AI [e.g., (Goodell et al. 2021; Wamba et al. 2021) ], multimodal data analysis [e.g., (Lu et al. 2023; Zhang et al. 2020a) ], and healthcare/medical [e.g., (Jimma 2023; Guo et al. 2020) ]."
